00:01:17.740 --> 00:01:28.107
But the set of issues under discussion introduces a symmetry breaking direction Z, that may be regarded as the simplest vector to characterize the society and what its members are discussing.

00:01:28.107 --> 00:01:36.500
We take this to be the direction parallel to the vector where all coordinates are 1, where all moral foundations are present and considered important.

00:01:36.500 --> 00:01:47.992
Our strategy then is to characterize both the state of the agents model and the empirical questionnaire data by introducing rotationally invariant order parameters which are semantically free as far as possible.

00:01:47.992 --> 00:01:53.097
